            <title>[LU-12443] sanity test_271f: @@@@@@ FAIL: expect 1 READ RPC,  occured</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-12443</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Test failure shows that read-on-open happens in case when it shouldn&apos;t. The reason is bigger reply buffer than test expects.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
